OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLineker tweet a technical  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbreach, ex-BBC head says   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An ex-BBC boss has said Gary Lineker's 
OL,6, criticism of the government's new      
OL,7, asylum bill appeared to be a "technical
OL,8, breach" of impartiality rules.         
OL,10,FBut Mark Thompson told the Sunday with 
OL,11,FLaura Kuenssberg programme that        
OL,12,FLineker's status as a sports presenter 
OL,13,Fmeant the row was a "grey area".       
OL,15,FHe said the BBC must "strike the       
OL,16,Fbalance" when enforcing the rules.     
OL,18,FThe BBC's football output remains in   
OL,19,Fchaos, with an unofficial staff boycott
OL,20,Fcontinuing into Sunday.                
